headline: Waste Management (WM) Upgraded to Outperform as Baird Sees Upside Potential Ahead
summary: Waste Management, Inc. (NYSE:WM) ranks among the stocks in Bill Gates’ portfolio that analysts are watching. On November 4, Baird raised its price target from $238 to $242 and upgraded Waste Management (NYSE:WM) from Neutral to Outperform. Despite several challenges, Baird was optimistic about Waste Management’s 2026 prospects, pointing out that the company’s present valuation […]

headline: Do Wall Street Analysts Like Waste Management Stock?
summary: Although Waste Management has underperformed the broader market over the past year, Wall Street analysts maintain a moderately optimistic outlook on the stock’s prospects.
